         <h4> How to use this app</h4>
        <p>
            From main page (Home) select category to browse words. From here you can:<br />
            - Add word to favourite list (plus icon).<br />
            - Listen to word pronunciation (using Forvo.com  API - internet connection required).<br />
            - Open word in external dictionary (click on link).<br /><br />
            From main menu you have access to favourite words list, search and add new translation form.<br />
            All new translations must wail for approval by administrator before use by app.<br />
            Additional menu can be open by menu button and there is possibility to switch external dictionary and 
            sync application database with server.<br /><br />
            Have fun.
        </p>
        <h4> Learnwords mobile web site and hybrid mobile app</h4>
        <p>
            Learnwords is web application built in HTML5 and Javascript. It is available under
            <a href='http://learnwords.tk/m'> learnwords.tk/m </a>.<br />
            It uses Backbone framework, JQuery and Bootstrap on client side and SLIM framework as Rest Server.
            <br />Supported browsers are: <br />
            - Mozilla Firefox <br />
            - Chrome <br />
            - Internet Explorer 10
        </p><br />
        Learnwords is also application for mobile phones.
        <p>
